                    <p>The Wyrd of Stromgard is a Dungeon World expansion inspired by the mythic lore of the Norse people. </p>
                    
                    <p>Heavily based on surviving Norse literary sources like the Poetic and Prose Eddas, Beowulf, and the Icelandic Sagas, Stromgard is a broad world of magic and titanic threats, of gods and monsters and oracles.  Above all, it is a world of discovery and heroism, of great opportunities for those wishing for the chance to prove their greatness.</p>

                    <p>The Wyrd of Stromgard provides an elaborate and detailed setting and, with the Dungeon World rules, epic Norse campaigns filled with gods, primal beasts, and bravery come together effortlessly.  Most importantly, Stromgard is a flexible setting and its playbooks can be used in tandem with the original classes of Dungeon World seamlessly.  The setting is rich and elaborate but it is designed to be alterable and customized to fit any game group's playstyle and interests.</p>
